     H            Y.
     F** SAVR02 ********************************************
     F*  PROGRAM: SAVE IMPORT DATA TO TAKWP01              *
     F*  WRITTEN: JW (SRA)  2021.03.11                     *
     F******************************************************
     FIMPORT  IF  F     200            DISK
     FIMPWP01 O   E                    DISK
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     IIMPORT  AA  01
     I                                        1 200 DATA
     I            DS
     I                                        1  140SDATE
     I                                        1   60NOW
     I                                        7  140TODAY
     I           SDS
     I                                        1   8 #PGM
     I                                      244 253 #WSID
     I                                      254 263 #USER
      *--------------------------------------------------------
      *                    MAIN PROCESS
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $FILE  10
     C                     PARM           $LIB   10
     C                     PARM           $PGM   10
      *
     C                     TIME           SDATE
      *
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     READ IMPORT                   98
     C   98                LEAVE
      *
     C                     Z-ADDTODAY     IMCRDT
     C                     Z-ADDNOW       IMCRTM
     C                     MOVEL#USER     IMCRUS
     C                     MOVEL#WSID     IMCRWS
     C                     MOVEL$FILE     IMFILE
     C                     MOVEL$LIB      IMLIB
     C                     MOVEL$PGM      IMCRPG
     C                     MOVELDATA      IMDATA
      *
     C                     WRITEIMPWP011
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
